Rating: 4
I try to like squash but am often disappointed with it. This recipe was impossible not to like. With the carmelized cinnamon onions, raisins and deeply-flavored almonds, the texture and taste combination was outstanding. I concur with the previous review; don't change anything. I made this with turban squash and was delighted.

